Kaizer Chiefs chairman Kaizer Motaung announced a new transport sponsorship from car manufacturer Toyota at the Soweto soccer giants' headquarters in Naturena outside Soweto on Wednesday.Toyota replace Nissan as Chiefs transport partner. These two iconic brands say a lot about being in a partnership Motaung said. We couldn t have chosen a better car sponsor than Toyota because they have a very large car manufacturing footprint in the country and they are one of the biggest car manufacturers in the world. Motaung said while the sponsorship was aimed directly at bolstering Chiefs resources on the field such partnerships are crucial to the overall success of the club.- TMG Digital/TMG Sport